io.zbox.zboxfs

Class Metadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.zbox.zboxfs.Metadata

  • public class Metadata
extends Object
    Metadata information about a regular file or a directory.

    This structure is returned from the File.metadata() and Repo.metadata(Path) represents known metadata about a regular file or a directory, such as its type, size, modification times, etc.
